name: Laharl
description: He's the heir of the Overlord. The so called fiercest demon in the Netherworld. But he's not good at dealing with busty women.

name: Killia
description: Supported by his friends, Killia has overcome his anger and sadness. No longer confused, his true power has already awakened.

name: Valvatorez
description: This young vampire is a Prinny Instructor. His favorite thing in is sardines. It's said that he's actually a very influential being.

name: Adell
description: He is a good young man who places great value on family. He has his own "style" and yields to no one. It is said that he is dating Rozalin.

name: Mao
description: He's the current Dean of Evil Academy. He has an EQ of 1.8 million and loves conducting evil research. He's also a remodeling maniac who loves to drizzle soy sauce on omelets.

name: Etna
description: She's Laharl's vassal and is known for her caustic tongue. She is a great admirer of the late King Krichevskoy. She runs through Prinnies as if they were paper napkins.

name: Fallen Angel Flonne
description: A former Apprentice Angel who fell from heaven for the crime of injuring another Angel. A love freak and Tokusatsu aficionado. Devoted to spreading the word of love, with somewhat mixed results...

name: Seraphina
description: The Gorgeous Overlord who has overcome her fear of poverty. Thanks to her newfound strength, she has become a fearless character. She has subtle romantic feelings for Killia.

name: Fuka
description: A middle school girl half transformed into a Prinny. She is unconvinced of her own death and thinks she's dreaming. She likes to rampage around with Desco.

name: Rozalin
description: A naive young lady. Now, she's learning all about the outside world, while living in harmony with Adell.

name: Axel
description: A family-oriented dark hero... and a dunce. He's got quite a lot of die hard fans who love his fanciful delusions and positive attitude when facing difficulties.

name: Fenrich
description: A young werewolf who serves Valvatorez. He has many schemes to improve his Master's position. "All is for my Lord" is his catchphrase.

name: Majorita
description: The Witch Who Controls Death, a former Demon General. She looks like a child, but her power rivals that of an Overlord.

name: Emizel
description: The only son of Hugo, the former President of the Netherworld. In order to become the President, he's busy doing his job as Death.

name: Barbara
description: A demon who was once an Overlord Candidate. The type of person who takes pride in faithfully carrying out orders, but is not good at acting on their own will.

name: Girl Laharl
description: Isn't it a tragedy?! A female Laharl. But the same autocratic egotist all the same. Her popularity has been soaring since the transformation.

name: Christo
description:
An Overlord from the Giant Netherworld... at least that is what he said.
As a peerless counselor and strategist,
he will do whatever it takes to achieve his goal.

name: Zeroken
description: An Overlord who has overcome his cowardice and timidness. An easily elated Ultimate Demon Technique user. He admires Killia as his senior disciple.

name: Red Magnus
description: The Overlord of Scorching Flame, where ruffians gather. He loves to say "Super", and has a super boorish personality. However, he also has a gentle side and cares for his subordinates.

name: Krichevskoy
description:
The Former Overlord and father to Overlord Laharl.
A wise leader, feared and loved by many demons for his charismatic nature.

name: Sicily
description: This girl is an angel from Celestia. She is strong-minded and hardworking, and good at cooking. It's said she likes Prinnies a lot.

name: Almaz
description: The Hero Wannabe has grown into a true Hero. Despite his cowardice, he's still practicing the "Hero's Oath". The Newly Married Hero!

name: Master Big Star
description:
魔立邪悪学園２号生のリーダーであり、
キラキラ輝く華麗な大スター。
「様」は敬称ではなく、名前の一部。

name: Salvatore
description:
The No.3 delinquent student in the Evil Academy, and one of the legendary "Diez Gentleman".
She loves to force others to carry out her whimsical orders, and very few can complete what she asks.

name: Sapphire
description: The princess of a human kingdom. She's still the "Killing Machine"  despite being married to Almaz. Her goal is to become "the strongest creature on earth."

name: Nemo
description:
A lonely soul born from a strong hatred towards humans.
He is being controlled by the terrifying King. It creates malicious intentions,
Use malicious intent to amplify your own power.

name: Bloodis
description: Former Demon General once known as the Great Demon Fist. His fists, which he uses with overwhelming power, can crush anything that stands in his way.

name: Nagi
description: She is a 14-year-old girl who utilizes mechanical techniques left behind by her father. She has a strong will to end all war.

name: Rutile
description: A kind girl who's a human-Nekomata hybrid. She possesses super strength despite her slender appearance.

name: Stella
class_name_3: The ONLY Daughter of the Dean
description: The daughter of a Majin who likes pulling pranks. She has really unique taste and fancies slimes and zombies.

name: Xenolith
description: A taciturn young demon. He has extraordinary magical power and such a cold attitude that no one dares to approach him.

name: Angel Apprentice Fron
description:
An angel apprentice respects Archangel Lamington.
He becomes a companion of Lahar to conduct love.

name: Pure Flonne
description: Flonne's awakened Archangel form, overflowing with the power of belief. The force of great love  has improved her abilities!

name: Archangel Flonne
description:
A very important Archangel who manages all the angels of Celestia.
She loves Tokusatsu more than anything and has even poured enormous amounts of money (HL) into the production of a giant robot.

name: Void Dark
description:
The most powerful Overlord who
brought all Netherworlds into war and has a troubled past with Killia.
To him, his sister's smiling face is his most precious treasure.

name: Artina
description: An Angel tasked by Celestia to collect money from the Netherworld. Doing her job too well has resulted in  Demons calling her the "Angel of Avarice".

name: Sister Artina
description: Artina when she was still alive as a human. Pure and innocent, she's saved the lives of countless soldiers.

name: Tyrant Valvatorez
description: A powerful vampire with the name of "Tyrant". He thinks the mission of demons is to strike fear into human hearts, and he takes pride in it. His goal is to become the avatar of terror.

name: Awakened Killia
description:
Killia, who has overcome his confusions and destructive urges,
and pushed the Ultimate Demon Technique
to its true limits.

name: Tyrant Overlord Killidia
description: Killia's visage when he was possessed by destructive impulses. Known as the Tyrant Overlord, he gives out  a terrifying evil aura that keeps others away.

name: 2P Etna
description:
Even if this is a different status
I think it's fine to stay like this
Without the basics and the basics
It's not a two-person etna in the first place

name: Majin Etna
description: Majin from another Netherworld. Her power rivals that of an Overlord. Her vicious roasts can burn people to a crisp.

name: Heroine Asagi
description:
The heroine of the game Disgaea Wars (Tentative),
a a determined girl who has dedicated to
defeating the Overlord and freeing the world from his clutches.

name: Gordon
description: The 37th Defender of Earth. Defeated by Laharl and made his vassal.

name: Jennifer
description: A genius who earned her doctorate at the age of 10. She made Thursday the robot at the age of 5.

name: Mr. Champloo
description:
An esteemed delinquent teacher
who has dedicated his ardor to cooking.
He is a master of the Grand Fire Chaos Punch.

name: Yukimaru
description: Kunoichi of Snow Melody Village who's known for adding "Zam" at the end of every sentence. The only flaw in her character is that  she feels responsible for every incident and is always trying to commit suicide.

name: Fubuki
description: Yukimaru's big brother. Devoted to the reconstruction  of Snow Melody Village. He's got a nice voice.

name: Awakened Rozalin
class_name_2: A Past That Must Be Forgotten
description: Rozalin, with the God of All Overlords' power awakened within her. She's surrounded by an ominous aura  that overwhelms her enemies.

name: Justice Fron
description:
Fron has awakened to the power of justice.
A hammer of justice to the evil of the demon world!

name: Pleinair
description: The mascot of Haradaya, the official website of Harada the character designer. Been working as the receptionist of the Dark Assembly for years.

name: Dark Santa Laharl
description: Changing into a Christmas costume  does not change Laharl's personality. Presents are not to be given away, they are to be taken away!

name: Noel
description: She is a Mage girl who longs to be Santa Claus. She's all dressed up and ready to go. Let's go distribute presents!

name: Attired Rozalin
class_name_5: Sinful Rose of the New Year
description: Rozalin, dressed in the traditional attire  of Snow Melody Village. She's very excited about having a Hatsumoude date  with Adell.

name: Pure Sicily
description: Sicily as the Magic Cutie of Love and Justice. She claims to feel embarrassed, but gets used to  the fluttery and frilly costume really fast.

name: Dark Artina
description: Artina as a Magic Cutie. Mysterious yet sexy, not bad at all.

name: Love Oracle
description: A Magic Cutie who claims to have been born in a dandelion. Boy, girl, who really cares?  What matters is we all love Magic Cuties!

name: Bunny Seraphina
description: Seraphina, the Gorgeous Overlord, has come for Easter in a bunny suit. It looks like she's looking for a capable servant!

name: Easter Mao
description: Mao in his Easter costume. The Easter Eggs he made with his 1.8 Million Evil Quotient... What is he going to do with them?

name: Gym Shorts Fuka
description: Fuka in short shorts is going to take part in the Fest-evil of Sport. She has no doubt she'll win because it's "in her dream". Nevertheless, she's still gonna put in the effort.

name: Ayame
description: The knight of steel who's been appointed the cheerleader of the Fest-evil of Sport. She likes to wear boys' uniform, and can't even sleep without it on.

name: Virunga
description: The Archangel who protects the order of Celestia with his own justice. Capable as he is, his values are a bit biased.

name: Torachiyo
description:
A battle-hardened adventurer
who has dedicated her entire life to rice balls.
She literally cares about nothing but rice balls. Someone calling out for the King of Rice Balls?!

name: Diez
description:
A self-proclaimed Fallen Angel Hunter who is terrible at acting.
A top-notch gunslinger, he will finish off his prey before they can even react.

name: Lucy
description:
A fallen angel who claims to be the best undercover investigator.
Although she knows what it takes to be an undercover agent,
she always thinks of just wiping out her enemies when her cover is blown.

name: Swimsuit Girl Laharl
description:
The same tragedy happened again? This time, even Girl Laharl was
forced to wear a swimsuit. She's taking out all her anger for
being converted into a busty hot girl!

name: Swimsuit Etna
description:
Etna who has put on a swimsuit to enjoy the sea.
Beach volleyball, parasol, and scuba...
Get everything ready before fully enjoying the sea. Come and have some fun! ♪

name: Swimsuit Flonne
description:
Flonne is in her swimsuit, ready for sea-bathing.
It seems she has regained her angel identity...Hmm?
You ask me why? Because that's the power of the swimsuit!!

name: Meaver
description:
A tough hunter who hunts monsters all over the Netherworld.
This time, the target is a monster in the sea.
She has changed to her swimsuit in order to keep her spirits high.

name: Marlene
description:
The owner of the Sea Club. Her Sea Club is always crowded, though Marlene hasn't realized that many of her customers only come to her club because of her. 
She is said to be a miser.

name: Fuka XENO
description:
A mysterious girl who looks like Fuka.
She has cut off her long hair due to some... well, very complicated reason.
But that story will be told another time...

name: Raspberyl XENO
description:
Another Raspberyl from another world.
She likes taking selfies with her "cellphone", an essential item for hotties
and then uploading the photos somewhere.

name: Yukata Valvatorez
description:
Valvatorez in his yukata, maintaining the order of the summer fest.
He really enjoys the Sardine Summer Fest he organizes.
In addition, he's asking everyone to greet each other with "Sardine!!"

name: Yukata Yukimaru
description:
Yukimaru wearing her yukata, looking forward to the summer fest.
Although the summer festival was not what she expected,
it was one of the best memories she had with her friends.

name: Hibana
description:
The ultimate firework engineer who applies Nether Science to her fireworks.
She doesn't care if her yukata gets messy
when she is totally absorbed in her firework research.

name: Meliodas
description:
The Dragon Sin of Wrath
and captain of the Seven Deadly Sins,
as well as the owner of the renowned tavern Boar Hat.

name: Elizabeth
description:
The third adoptive princess
of the Kingdom of Liones has a caring heart.

name: Ban
description:
The Fox Sin of Greed of the Seven Deadly 
Sins,known for his fox-patterned tattoo
and his immortality.

name: Diane
description:
The Serpent Sin of Envy of the Seven Deadly 
Sins,a member of the Giant Clan.

name: Gowther
description:
The Goat Sin of Lust of the Seven 
Deadly Sins.

name: Cutie Demon Elizabeth
description:
Elizabeth who is wearing Etna's costume,
ready for a fashion contest in another world.
Her determination is unstoppable!

name: Liones Princess Etna
description:
Etna who is wearing Elizabeth's costume,
ready for a fashion contest in another world.
This actually... looks great!

name: Merlin
description:
The Boar Sin of Gluttony of the Seven Deadly 
Sins.She is regarded as the greatest 
sorceress in Britannia.

name: King
description:
The Grizzly Sin of Sloth of the Seven Deadly 
Sins,and the king of fairies.

name: Cute Flonne
description:
The much-loved leader of the Cutie V!
With a heart of love and justice, Cute Flonne
has been spreading the greatness of love to the entire world.

name: Cute Chacha
description:
A reserve member of the Cutie V
who loves living a carefree life. After hearing that she could enjoy as much catnip
and other snacks as she pleases, she joined the Cutie V.

name: Cute Mei Ling
description:
A reserve member of the Cutie V,
she will add mustard sauce to whatever she eats. Her love for mustard sauce is so overwhelming
that she has even invented her own spells to protect it.

name: Mao XENO
description:
Another Mao from another world.
He has invented his own evil gymnastics
and will work out whenever he's idle. By the way, he's nicknamed "Mao Mao".

name: Halloween Majorita
description:
Majorita in disguise as a witch.
She wants to fully enjoy herself
with her most creative Halloween pranks.

name: Halloween Artina
description:
A blood-stained angel descends on Halloween night.
The costume and all accessories are made by Artina herself.
※And of course, the blood is fake, too.

name: Halloween Laharl
description:
Laharl who has been turned into a Frankenstein by Jennifer.
He buzzes like the real Frankenstein!

name: Zed
description: A zombie boy who uses a teleportation spell called "Super Reincarnation" to travel across Netherworlds on his quest to defeat the God of Destruction. He will never give up even if he dies thousands of times.

name: Majolene
description: A great witch, as well as the principal of the Magimage School of Magic. She uses the legendary Magical Wand of Transformation to become Magic Cutie ☆ Majolene and kick butt!!

name: Attired Killia
description:
To commemorate the first anniversary of Disgaea RPG, Killia has put on the attire Seraphina ordered for him.
This outfit is actually perfect for strenuous exercise.

name: Attired Seraphina
description:
Seraphina wearing her attire to commemorate
the first anniversary of Disgaea RPG.
Her gown is expensive enough to buy a dozen Netherworlds.

name: Thunderlord Laharl
description:
Another Laharl who wields the power of lightning, known as "Thunderlord".
His serious disposition makes him not really look like a demon.
It seems he comes to this Netherworld for his beloved sister Sicily.

name: Sicily XENO
description: Another Sicily from another world, who has dressed as an Overlord. She doesn't appear to be fond of her meddlesome brother Laharl, but in fact...

name: Santa Adell
description:
Adell has become stronger thanks to the Christmas Power granted by Noel.
His bag is filled with gifts for his cherished ones.

name: Santa Rozalin
description:
Encouraged by her childhood friend Tink, Rozalin puts on her Christmas costume and attends a Christmas party.
Although she’s a bit embarrassed, she is looking forward to Adell's reaction.

name: Attired Girl Laharl
description: For Laharl, this is the ultimate disaster! Once again, he has been turned into a girl. As an Overlord, she intentionally messed up her attire as her form of protest.

name: Maiden Sicily
description:
Sicily who has accepted Prinny God's divine power and awakened.
Her new power allows her to skillfully control her shikigami, helping her brother who is in distress.

name: Tyrant Overlord Laharl
description:
Laharl unleashes his full potential and becomes the Tyrant Overlord.
With his unbridled power, ambition and wildness, he is more than competent as the ruler of the Netherworld.

name: Melodia
description:
A princess from the musical world
who has been waiting for her Prince Charming
and longing for her happy ending.

name: Ivar
description:
The self-proclaimed greatest Overlord in the entire universe.
Despite his stupidity that denies him any respect, he does possess amazing power.
By the way, he likes Bieko the most.

name: Emilia
description: A beautiful half-elf girl with silver hair and bluish-purple eyes, the same as the "Witch of Envy" who once almost destroyed the world.

name: Rem
description: Survivor of the demons who have the strongest power among the demi-humans. She is a maid girl who handles all the chores in the mansion where Emilia and her friends live.

name: Ram
description: Rem's elder twin sister, who once had unparalleled power as a demon child prodigy. She has lost her horn of power and is now a maid like Rem.

name: Sweet Omega
description:
A Love Laboratory lead actress who specializes in school romances.
She has given many men bitter-sweet memories and is an expert on youthful romance.

name: Prier
description:
An active tomboy and a new sister of the La Pucelle who was raised in an orphanage after losing her parents at a young age.
Her dream is to become a Saint of Light.

name: Croix
description:
A freelance exorcist who doesn't belong to any church.
He accompanies Prier and her friends to try and regain his lost memories.
A cheerful and reliable individual.

name: Alouette
description:
A nun in charge of educating Prier and Culotte as their senior in La Pucelle.
Her strong religious devotion can at times lead to a rigid inflexibility.

name: Eclair
description:
Princess of the Kingdom of St. Paprika who is burdened by the high expectations of those around her.
She refers to Prier as "my lady".

name: Bieko
description:
Pure and kind-hearted sister of Zed.
She fondly calls him "Buddy" and morally supports him as he challenges the God of Destruction.

name: Piyori
description:
Leader of the Prism Rangers.
Ever since she was defeated by the God of Destruction and abandoned by her comrades, she is always attempting to recruit new members.

name: Misedor
description:
A wealthy king of the human world.
He squanders his fortune recklessly and tries to solve every problem with money.

name: Evil Rebirth Mao
description:
As a result of the super hero's wicked strategies, an evilness took control of Mao, causing him to rampage as he fell to Asura.
No one, not even the super hero can stop him now...

name: Emizel XENO
description: Even in this alternative dimension, Emizel secured the position of an Elite Officer within XENO thanks to the help of his parents' connections. He is currently under stress from subordinates who don't listen to him.

name: Frostlord Rozalin
description:
One of the Holy Defenders who was summoned from another dimension.
She carries the title of "Frostlord," but under the appearance of the majestic ice queen, there is also a careless side.

name: Flamelord Majorita
description: She controls fire, and as one of the Holy Defenders carries the title of "Flamelord". A berserker through and through.

name: Merome
description:
A zombie girl who loves horror, yet is afraid of ghosts.
She has robbed the hearts of countless men visiting the Love Laboratory by grasping onto their arms and screaming, "Eeek, I'm scared!"

name: Mikasa
description:
A soldier in the Survey Corps.
She showed overwhelming talent in combat even as a new recruit.
She wields her blades to protect those she cares about.

name: Levi
description:
Squad captain within the Survey Corps.
He is widely known as humanity's strongest soldier and has a track record of killing countless Titans.

name: Calamity Adell
description:
Adell is consumed by loneliness after killing the one he loved.
No matter how much meat and blood he feasts on, his hunger is never truly satisfied...

name: Swimsuit Fuka
description:
Fuka is enjoying herself at the beach.
She loves her new white swimsuit, and her sun visor was handmade by Valvatorez and his friends.

name: Swimsuit Lucy
description:
As a result of working hard undercover on an isolated island, she got a tan.
There is no way whatsoever she was just enjoying herself the whole time...

name: Amane
description:
A maiden appeared on this desert island, one who loves and lives in the sea.
She has traversed many seas, sometimes getting tossed about by raging waves.

name: Tyrant Overlord Etna
description:
Etna became a Tyrant Overlord after defeating the biggest badass in the Netherworld.
But being an Overlord was just a stepping stone for her.
The legend of Cutie Tyrant Overlord Etna begins here and now!

name: Zetta
description:
The strongest Overlord in all the universe.
He has made a name for himself throughout the Netherworlds by dominating with his powerful magic.

name: Petta
description:
Overlord Zetta's daughter who arrived from the future.
She is earnest, polite, and very honest.
She seems ecstatic to be participating in the tournament with her parents.

name: Plum
description:
An Overlord who is said to possess extraordinary magical talent, the power of prophesy, and the respect of the other Overlords.
She enjoys playing with her favorite toys.

name: Salome
description:
A former disciple of Overlord Zetta, and the mother of Petta.
A witch who abandoned her humanity and descended into the Underworld Labyrinth.
Find out more in "Phantom Kingdom"!

name: Siedl
description:
Ruler of the Underworld, where the dead gather.
He was once was a hero known as the Samurai in the human world.
He apparently has unresolved issues with Salome from when he was still a human.

name: Wise
description:
An all-knowing and all-powerful Sage of the Netherworld that manages the Depository facility.
She proclaims herself to be all-knowing and all-powerful, however...

name: Keke
description:
An eccentric sorcerer who manages the Prinny Workshop where you can refine equipment.
Although he may appear tricky, he is actually a sweetheart.

name: Timmy
description:
One of the few top breeders of the Netherworld.
He is a passionate Beastmaster of monsters, well-versed in the caring of Innocent.

name: Aiko
description:
A female combat android.
She is a multi-talented android who can cook, do the laundry, fight, and even manage the Request Board.

name: 鹿目まどか
description:
異世界からやって来た中学２年生の少女。 
現在は魔法少女として 
日々魔女や使い魔と戦っている。

name: 美樹さやか
description:
まどかの同級生、かつ親友であり、
まどか達とともに魔法少女として
魔女と戦っている。

name: 巴マミ
description:
学校ではまどか達の先輩で 
お姉さんのような存在であり、 
面倒見の良いベテランの魔法少女。

name: 佐倉杏子
description:
赤いポニーテールが印象的な 
槍使いの魔法少女。 
利己的なところもあるが、義理堅く情け深い。

name: 暁美ほむら
description:
容姿端麗、才色兼備でクールな魔法少女。 
謎が多く、排他的な雰囲気を持つが、 
胸に秘めた思いは人一倍強い。

name: 魔法少女ラハール
description:
リモート暗黒議会の力により、ロリっ子な
魔法少女になってしまったラハール。
その魔力はもちろん魔王級！

name: Tavern Mascot Flonne
description:
Flonne who became a waitress at the Boar Hat in order to participate in an intergalactic Fashion Contest.
She is pretty psyched about it!

name: Kagemaru
description:
Another Yukimaru who arrived from an alternate dimension.
He attempts to solve every issue by killing under the pretext of "assisted death."

name: 未来戦士プレネール
description:
なんと２０００周年の時代から
現代にやってきたプレネールさん。
未来でも『原田屋』の看板娘はもちろん彼女だ。

name: 提督ロザリンド
description:
未来のバトルスーツを身に付けたロザリンド。
勇ましいその姿は提督の貫禄。
颯爽とアデルの危機に立ち向かう。

name: 未来ウサリア
description:
プレネールさんの暴走を止めるため
未来からやってきたウサリア。
未来では兎兎魔界を立派に治めているとか。

name: 礼装ヴァルバトーゼ
description:
『ディスガイアＲＰＧ』２周年をお祝いするため
エレガントな装いに身を包んだヴァルバトーゼ。
３年目も彼とイワシの活躍に刮目せよ！

name: 礼装アルティナ
description:
『ディスガイアＲＰＧ』２周年記念用にと誂えた
礼装姿のアルティナ。天使長から贈られた品で、
その財源は……今は考えない事にしているとか。

name: 日本一ちゃん
description:
愛と勇気で悪を討つ！
正義のヒーロー、日本一！
魔界の平和はアタシが守る！

name: サンタセラフィーヌ
description:
金と権力を惜しみなく使い、
特注の衣装を作らせたセラフィーヌ。
この衣装でキリアを悩殺する予定。

name: サンタ虎千代
description:
クリスマスと聞いてなぜか
紅い甲冑を身にまとった虎千代。
みんなにおにぎりをプレゼントするのだ！

name: 超魔王ラハールちゃん
description:
魔王の頂点、超魔王となったラハールちゃん。
ムチプリになろうとも内に秘められたパワーは
変わらず、誰も止めることはできない。

name: 晴れ着エトナ
description:
初詣のために晴れ着を新調したエトナ。 
槍と一体化したマイクは、 
１０８の願いを叫ぶための特注品だ！

name: リューベンス
description:
ツギハギだらけで寡黙な「南瓜の魔女」。
常に自動筆記で何かが書き込まれ続けている
本を持ち歩いている。

name: 魔王式メタリカ
description:
ラハールちゃんの衣装を纏ったメタリカ。
溢れんばかりの最凶魔王の力を使って
魔界を沼に沈めようと企んでいる。

name: 洗脳マジョリタ
description:
禁断の魔術書『ホレ・テマウ』の力によって
洗脳されブルカノに惚れてしまったマジョリタ。
度々正気に戻っては己の惨状に頭を抱えている。

name: Black Rabbit Usa
description: A black-clad Usalia from another dimension. Due to her lack of positive emotions, she always coldly and impartially carries out her missions. *t/l note: This character's JP name is simply "U", but for clarity's sake, we'll be using "Usa" until official localization.

name: White Rabbit Salia
description: A white-clad Usalia from another dimension. Due to her lack of negative emotions, she tends to innocently yet violently play with her enemies with a smile...

name: Great Demon Fist Lieze
class_name_5: She That Surpasses the Golden Lion
description: A Liezerota from another dimension. After returning from hundreds of years of hellish training, she was seen as an entirely new individual, known to the masses as the Great Demon Fist..."

name: Seraphina XENO
description: A Seraphina from another dimension. Normally, she's lacking in self-confidence and ostentatious, but whenever Killia XENO's involved...
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Sapphire XENO
description: A Sapphire from another dimension. The Boss of the Hell's Allies biker gang, who all fell in love with her strength under pressure, like a true man. The volunteers just keep lining up to join!

name: Summoner Adell
description: An Adell from another dimension. Trained in the arts of summoning from his mother, he's grown into the ultimate summoner.

name: Yasuko
description: A girl that attends Majin Academy. As a chairman of the student council, her motto is to fight dirty and with extreme prejudice. She is living her unscrupulous demonic school life to the fullest.

name: Maid Salvatore
description: Salvatore has been accepted into Majin Academy's Maid program, tempted by being able to give orders to both customers and masters as much as she wants. Her culinary specialty is the "Lovey-Dovey Omelette Rice".

name: Crowned Valvatorez
description: Valvatorez, having hit first place in the DISGAEA RPG Popularity contest, won this majestic crown.

name: Eren
description: A boy who dreams of the world outside the walled city. He has an extraordinary hatred for the Titans that causes him to be reckless.

name: Survey Corps Fuka
description: Fuka dons the jacket of the Survey Corps and is enthusiastic about destroying Titans. But she has zero intention of devoting herself to the Corps.

name: Super Hero Asagi
class_name_5: She who Fights with the Overlord
description: The once-defeated hero Asagi was ressurrected, together with the power of Overlord Asagi. A true hero will rise again and again, anytime!

name: Asagiri Asagi
description: The male Asagi created by HGC Asagi to be the main character of an action game. He uses pointlessly stylish attacks to defeat his enemies!

name: Prinny Mascot Asagi
description: A mysterious Asagi wearing a Prinny Mascot costume. While she tries hard, she's not good at playing a Prinny and often forgets her lines need to contain "dood".

name: Asagi Koigiri
description: The popular heroine of Asagi Memorial, a romance game created by Creator Asagi. She's quite particular about her glasses.

name: Fighter Asagi
description: The main character of the fighting game, "Asagi Fighters." Her martial arts creed is to always seek out stronger and stronger opponents.

name: Groom Almaz
description: Almaz dressed as a groom for the Bridal Grand Prix. He's always happy to walk down the aisle at Sapphire's side.

name: Bride Sapphire
description: Sapphire dressed up for the Bridal Grand Prix. With this dress, her love power for Almaz increases 100 times over!

name: Bride Seraphina
description: Seraphina dressed up for the Bridal Grand Prix. It seems this dress is just as expensive as the Great Flonzor X giant robot... or more!
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Bride Rozalin
description: Rozalin dressed up for the Bridal Grand Prix. Her dress was tailor-made for her by Hanako and Sapphire.

name: Primeval Overlord Killia
description: The ultimate Tyrant Overlord who seized the title of "The Strongest" during the ancient Netherworld War era.

name: Infinite Reincarnation Zed
description: After Super Reincarnating a nearly infinite amount of times, Zed's power has exceeded its limits and grown unstoppable.

name: Nagisa
description: A researcher of the legend of the Holy Swimsuit. The shackles on her wrists and ankles seem to increase her mana power.

name: Beach Artina
description: Artina, enthusiastic to show off her new swimsuit on the white sand beach! But sadly, Valvatorez is busy setting up the Sardine Festival elsewhere...

name: Beach Saint Etna
description: Saint Etna suddenly ended up clad in the Holy Swimsuit of Legend. The embarassment is plain on her cheeks.

name: Super Pure Flonne
description: Pure Flonne, having gained even more of the Power of Love, transformed into a Super Awakened Angel. She'll crush all evil with this new overwhelming Power of Love!

name: Summer Fenrich
description: While he looks a bit rough in his cool summer clothes, the difference between his normal cold smile and the genuine smile he shows his master causes many to swoon.

name: Summer Piyori
description: This scorching hero of justice takes time off to be a bug-catching expert for the demonic summer. The plastic cage contains the newest member of the team, Prism Stag Beetle!

name: Transformed Thursday
description: Thursday with a new body and advanced emotion software based on schematics from Genjuro Kazamatsuri. The long blonde hair seems to be detachable.

name: Curator Mao
class_name_5: Absolute Ruler of the Manji Festival
description: Mao has become the curator of the Netherworld Manji Tech Expo, a dream of his since childhood. The cane he carries contains the power of a superhero.

name: Majin Hanako
description: Hanako's future self in 10 years, having earned the title of Majin. While she didn't get the dynamite body she expected, she did gain a considerable amount of power.

name: Thunderlady Laharl
description: Thunderlord Laharl was accidentally transformed into a woman by the malfunctioning Transmigration Machine. Even as a Thunderlady, Laharl's combat power is as strong as ever.

name: RK Girl Laharl
description: Transformed by the Sacred Tome into the image of the most cringe-inducing fool in the cosmos, Royal King Drake. But Laharl makes the most of it and remains stronger than ever!

name: Alexander
description: Zetta's self-proclaimed rival and nemesis. He's always challenging Zetta to epic final battles, but there's never a clear winner.

name: Atrocious Overlord Petta
description: In this form, Petta has accumulated three powers at once: the power of a Time Traveller, a Freakin' Badass Overlord, and an Atrocious Overlord!

name: Trenia
description: A mysterious girl who has a deep connection with the Sacred Tome, and whose mysterious nature even Pram cannot predict.

name: Overlord Pram
description: The true form of Pram the Oracle when she unleashes all her Mana power. Her overwhelming aura of power freezes everything nearby.

name: Badass Overlord Etna
class_name_5: Most Badass Little Devil in All the Universes
description: Etna steals the power of Zetta's eyes along with his outfit. This doubles the power of her Sexy Beam, making her the Most Badass Beauty Queen in the Cosmos!

name: Brave Laharl
description: Laharl's new form when awakened by the Power of a Hero from Future Warrior Pleinair.

name: Shadowshark Overlord Pleinair
description: A future Pleinair, who has gained the power to manipulate time and space. She has turned into an Overlord who travels between the future, the past, and parallel worlds.

name: First Lady Etna
description: Etna when enchanted by Shadowshark Overlord Pleinair. At first she seemed brainwashed, but actually Etna thought the role of top villainess suited her pretty well so she went along willingly.

name: Young Rozalin
description: A version of Rozalin who was drained of her mana power by Shadowshark Overlord Pleinair and became younger. When Adell carries her on his back, she immediately becomes sleepy like a little kid.

name: Formal Lieze
description: Liezerota dressed in glittering formal attire. The dress seems to be a custom-made outfit Seraphina ordered from Gorgeous.

name: Brave Flonne
description: Flonne transformed into a hero using armor given to her by Future Usalia. Her chest looks big, but the inside of the armor is hollow.

name: Santa Future Usalia
description: Learning of an otherworldly Dark Santa's rampage in the past, Future Usalia dressed as Santa and rushed to save the timeline on Christmas Eve.

name: Dark Yule Sicily Xeno
description: The self-proclaimed Overlord Sicily from another world. Dressed in a jet-black Santa outfit, she sews chaos on the holy night of winter.

name: Santa Nisa
description: To avenge the evil that plagues the holidays! A hero of justice, Nisa, shall protect the Yuletide of the Netherworld!

name: Dark Santa Noel
description: A once-innocent fangirl for Santa... but due to Sicily XENO's Dark Yule Power, she was transformed into a vicious advocate of Dark Santa instead.

name: Zodiac Lucy
class_name_3: Fallen Angel in the Year of the Rabbit
description: Lucy, who gained the power of the year of the rabbit and became the main character of this year. Investigators are of course working during the year-end and New Year holidays! According to her, she is still undercover during the New Year's visit.

name: Priestess Melodia
description: Melodia dressed in a dancer-like costume as an unorthodox shrine maiden. She plans to propose to Zed again with this new style.

name: New Year Frostlord Rozalin
description: Frostlord Rozalin, dressed in a festive outfit. Her heart and stomach are racing with excitement at her New Year's date with Summoner Adell.

name: Majin Pram
description: Pram in Etna's costume. Possessing the power of a Beauty Queen and a genius Overlord. No one can stop her.

name: Marona
description: A 13-year-old girl with the mysterious power to manipulate spirits (phantoms). People around her call her "demon possessed" because of her abilities.

name: Ash
description: The phantom of a young man from another world. He is kind and has a strong sense of justice, and makes it his mission to protect Marona.

name: Dark Eclair
class_name_4: Black Knight of the Dark Night
description: Another personality that lives in Éclair's heart. She is the complete opposite of the normal saintly Éclair, and has a chaotic personality.

name: Hell Prisoner Salvatore
description: An inmate imprisoned in the deepest depths of Hell. An immortal prisoner who has survived 30,000 executions.

name: Artina XENO
description: Artina from another world who became a thrall after having her blood sucked by Valvatorez, the Nightmare Tyrant. She works as his nurse and maid and follows her master's orders.

name: Shinelord Axel
description: A super narcissistic Axel from another world. He is one of the Holy Guardians, but unlike the other Axel, he has tremendous power.

name: Holy Thunderlord Laharl
description: A Laharl from another world who was temporarily granted the power of the Saint to fulfill Saint Etna's wish. This power is wielded to protect the ones who matter most.

name: Fuji
description: A rogue samurai who rejected the Bushido tenets of the Hinomoto Netherworld Cluster. He is self-diagnosed with an "Empathy Allergy", and if explosed to high amounts of friendship, affection, or sympathy, begins to cough up considerable amounts of blood.

name: Higan Zesshosai
description: The latest to hold the title of Hinomoto's Strongest Swordsman, "Zesshosai". She is Fuji's sword master and has recently given up her sword and gotten into spear-wielding. Her love of rich sweets is unmatched.

name: Flonne Zesshosai
description: Taking after her favorite Dark Samurai B-Movie action hero, "KatanaMan", Flonne has studied the blade. This custom-made KatanaMan cosplay was designed by Pirilika.

name: Pirilika
description: A somewhat ditzy girl from the Wahei Netherworld. She's an extreme Hinomoto fangirl with a rose-colored view of what Bushido is. But she persists in trying to get everyone she can to embrace it!

name: Ao
description: Fuji's daughter who adores her dad. She was once feared as the "Ice Fang Princess" for her repeated destructive incidents in the Hinomoto Netherworld Cluster.

name: Desco X
description: Making use of their rage and their newfound sisterly bond, Desco and Des X have fused into a new form. Their combined power has increased their size temporarily to look about the same age as their big sister Fuka.

name: Starblade Sicily XENO
class_name_5: Ruin Overlord of the Twin Blades
description: Sicily XENO when clad in the manifested equipment of her Original Character, do not steal. The backstory behind her dual-wielded blades is extensive enough to fill multiple notebooks!

name: Nightmare Tyrant Valvatorez
description: Valvatorez from another world. It is said that all who gaze upon his ethereal form come to fear and admire him. All, that is, except the one man who defeated him...

name: Fire Fist Flamelord Majorita
description: A powered up form of one of the four Holy Guardians, the Flamelord, but specialized in using clawed fist attacks. While the power boost is immense, the exhaustion of maintaining this form is equally difficult.

name: Demon Detective Girl Laharl
description: A demonic detective who seems just as likely to cause a murder as to solve one, earning the nickname "the Blue Shinigami". Laharl decides to use brains instead of brawn to hunt down today's culprit... hopefully!

name: Onigiri Detective Torachiyo
description: There is always only one Truth, just like there should always be only one filling for a riceball! This is the motto of the Great Detective who can solve any impossible case, the Onigiri Detective Torachiyo!

name: Aileen
description: A new maid at Laharl's castle. She's polite, has a gentle personality, and is even good at cooking. She's perfect as a maid. But her favorite thing is a S-E-C-R-E-T.

name: Transcendent Adell
description: A new form achieved by spending countless hours training to the limit within the Mental Time Chamber. These peak performance muscles are the crystallization of his desire to protect those he loves.

name: Beach Seraphina
description: Seraphina in a custom made swimsuit. Designed with the goal of catching Sir Killia's eye. It seems that the cost of this swimsuit could buy an entire Netherworld.
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Beach Rozalin
description: Rozalin when she joins the swimming lessons camp to overcome her tendency to sink like a hammer in water. This swimsuit seems more designed for lounging than exercise though...

name: Beach Valvatorez
description: Valvatorez when seeking to overcome a vampire's innate weakness to flowing water. This sardine-themed hoodie has quickly become his favorite summer outfit.

name: Beach Usalia
description: Usalia having joined the swimming lessons camp. Her goal this summer is to overcome the reliance on her old friend, the floatie innertube, and venture off on her own to enjoy some beach house seafood curry.

name: Beach Fallen Angel Flonne
description: Flonne when possessed by the Legendary Holy Swimsuit. The swimsuit warps her personality to be more like a real Fallen Angel's, so she acts a little more sultry than usual.

name: Ceefore
description: Known across Hinomoto as the Chivalric Thief, Mouse★Girl. She's obsessed with weapons, explosions, and sniffing gunpowder, which if she goes too long without doing, will negatively affect her health.

name: Yeyasu
description: The Shogun of the Hinomoto Netherworld Cluster. A bit of a narcissist and a womanizer, his personality can cause trouble. Still, he has a knack for handling Infernal Treasures.

name: Beach Pirilika
description: A pure-hearted young CEO enjoying her summer vacation. Pirilika is especially enjoying developing new special moves on the sands with her friends Flonne and Higan, who are always in the same mindset as her.

name: Beach Higan Zesshosai
description: The Netherworld's strongest swordsman, known as the "Zesshosai" enjoying a relaxing summer. Though she's on vacation with Pirilika, she never skips a day of training, but she also won't pass up a chance at some seasonal sweets while she's at it!

name: Bunny Meaver
description: Meaver all dressed up in the traditional garb of Toto Bunny to celebrate the Harvest Moon Festival. She's just excited to be included!

name: Bunny Liezerota
class_name_5: Majestic Blossom of the Harvest Moon
description: Liezerota in traditional rabbit attire for attending the Toto Bunny Harvest Moon Festival. She's a bit shy about showing off so much skin, but she's enjoying having a matching outfit with Seraphina.

name: Harvest Moon Frostlord Rozalin
description: Frostlord Rozalin dons the traditional Toto Bunny attire to travel all the way to that Netherworld's Harvest Moon Festival. Her goal: The limited edition Moonfest Curry Dango!

name: Mizuki
description: A graduate of magic school who used to be Summoner Adell's school mate. He has a knack for mind-altering magic. Due to this immense talent, he is known as the "Untouchable Super Genius Mage."

name: Wild Fenrich
description: Fenrich's werewolf blood is out of control due to the heightened power of the harvest moon, so his fighting prowess and hair volume have drastically increased. Don't call him a Doggie or a Fluffy Butler if you like all your limbs where they are.

name: Magic Knight Marine
description: Marine the Beach Shop Owner in her casual clothes. Though she's a warrior, she's also skilled at magic, making her a rarity among demons.

name: Jiangshi Hanako
description: Hanako dressed up for Halloween. She made the costume herself, taking a whole month of work. Her specialty is imitating a Jiangshi (Chinese hopping vampire) whose warding ofuda charms have been removed.

name: Witch Etna
description: Etna in her costume for Halloween. It seems the costume took well over 10 billion HL to create, so Etna treats it with great care. How un-Etna-like!

name: Cute Devil Beryl XENO
description: Raspberyl XENO dressed up in a Halloween costume. The sexy and cute devilish style aims to captivate the attention of men and women alike.

name: Main Hero B
description: The most eccentric of the Celestial Hosts. He experiences pain as pleasure. "Main Hero B" is just a stage name, but nobody's ever given him the chance to say his real one. Now he just accepts it. Also, he's a man.

name: Angel Lucy
class_name_5: Heart of Gold Masked Behind Serious Glasses
description: By the power of Archangel Pleinair, Lucy has turned back into a full-fledged angel. She's never late, never absent, never slacking off. In fact, she's happy to work overtime! This Lucy is a devoted, benevolent angel who always works diligently.

name: Formal Usalia
description: Usalia in formalwear prepared especially for the 4th anniversary. The outfit was made-to-order and she's excited to join the party in matching outfits with her friends.

name: Holy Angel Rozalin
description: Rozalin became an angel through the power of the Legendary Angel. Her dazzling light illuminates the world and is said to heal all who gaze upon it. She finds the angel attire a little embarassing though.

name: Fallen Angel Sicily
description: The Angel Sicily has finally become a fallen angel! She's aiming to be a real bad girl! ...But she's having trouble, since she's naturally such a good girl. She refers to Laharl by new nicknames, hoping to sound cool. It's not really working.

name: Archangel Pleinair
description: An ephemeral angel that appears when people's wishes are gathered. It seems that the four wings have the power to grant any wish, and one can receive blessings just by touching them.

name: Demonic Angel Girl Laharl
description: Laharl became a darker kind of angel with the ephemeral Archangel's power. It's if Laharl's subconscious is the reason he became a woman in this form, or if it was the wishes of more unsavory residents of the Netherworlds.

name: Yule Black Rabbit Usa
class_name_3: Black Twin of the Yule Moon
class_name_5: Black Moon Piercing the Silent Night
description: Usa dressed in a jet black holiday outfit. Only worn at her sister's insistence, it's actually not a bad fit. It seems to come equipped with a stealth mode option.

name: Santa Ao
description: Ao dressed in a handmade Santa costume. Pirilika's sewing techniques and Ao's exuberance at wearing the costume are the real holiday gifts on display here.

name: Holy Demon Fist Liezerota
description: Holy Demon Fist Lieze wearing a Santa costume. She has started training young demons at the "Slaughter Claus Dojo" in order to deliver evil presents to children.

name: Yule White Rabbit Salia
class_name_3: White Twin of the Yule Moon
class_name_5: White Moon Dancing in the Silent Night
description: Salia dressed in a pure white holiday outfit. Her spirits are lifted 10 billion percent when this is worn alongside her twin in matching attire. It seems to come equipped with a dirt-repelling system.

name: Casualwear Noel
description: An upbeat witch who aspires to be like Santa Claus. Even her casual clothes are themed with holiday colors since she looks forward to Netherworld Christmas every day.

name: Santa Fuka
description: Much to her annoyance, Fuka ends up wearing a too-short makeshift Santa costume that's useless for the cold. According to her, "No one would choose to wear something like this in winter!"

name: New Year Salvatore
description: Salvatore dressed in order-made casual attire for the New Year. It's perfect for increasing freedom of movement, allowing her to dodge bullets and even the dangers of spilled curry soup!

name: Zodiac Higan Zesshosai
description: The deadliest swordsfighter, Higan Zesshosai, absorbed the power of the deadliest dragon of the Zodiac. Her newly-heightened powers are so great, it is thought that she can destroy anything in creation with a single blow.

name: New Years Pram
description: Pram dressed in her finest New Year's attire. The golden brush she holds is said to grant any wishes written with it and to bring its user good fortune.

name: Priestess Bieko
description: Bieko dressed up in an adorable shrine maiden costume. Zed said that the combo of her innocent heart and unbeatably cute priestess costume make her look super strong...!

name: Patissier Raspberyl
description: A substitute home ec teacher who burns with a passion for love and cooking. It seems she studied to get her Netherworld Chef's License all for the sake of helping out the girl students who had no clue what to do for Valentine's Day.

name: School Uniform Melodia
description:
Melodia in her school uniform.
She is the lone diva and the top raw slaughter in the school's caste.
Numerous men have been dumped by her. ......

name: School Uniform Seraphina
description: Seraphina in a sailor-style school uniform. She's dressed the part of a classic childhood friend unable to take things to the next level with her long-time crush.
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: School Uniform Artina
description: Artina in a sailor-style school uniform. She's dressed the part of a student to take classes from a certain delinquent teacher she has a crush on.

name: Breezy Satina
description: One of the legendary Diez Gentlemen of Evil Academy and the head girl of the educational program. While she looks cute and cheerful, she's really a devious Honor Student. What happened to her former Sabercat partner...?

name: Valentine Flonne
description: Flonne, now merged with the Ultimate Demon Passion Love Cells mk.3! Her boundless reservoir of love energy supposedly rivals over 1 million Love Big Bangs.

name: Visco
description: Her full name is Viscole Dotrish. A knight of the Amataya Kingdom and an inquisitor of heresy. Afflicted by a bestial transmogrification curse, she has been partially transformed into a dog.

name: Lavily Lalula La
description: Usually goes by "Lavi". She has the title of "Flame Witch" and is known to be the most naturally gifted apprentice of the Walpurgis coven. Her familiar is a rabbit doll named "Lord Bunnikins."

name: Malia
class_name_5: Merciful Great Witch of the Deep Green
description: The Forest Witch who has claimed to be Metallia's mother. Despite Metallia's unkind actions towards her, like calling her a 'snake' or a 'scorpion', she continues to always watch over her daughter.

name: Majin Metallia
description: Having become interested in experiments to fuse the powers of Demons and Witches, Metallia crafted a form to utilize Etna's Majin powers. The costume shows off 150% more than on Etna.

name: Freyja
description: The Goddess of Nature and Fertility from the world of the Gods, "Valhalla", who works under the chief god, Odin the All-Father. She's also renown as the top deadpan snarker of the game "Yurudrasil".

name: Valkyrie
description: The protagonist of the game "Yurudrasil" ("RagnaQuest" in the West). She is a valkyrie chosen by the goddess Freyja who travels the realms wherever her aid is needed. She's known to have such an immense sweet tooth that she even puts tons of sugar in bitter genmaicha tea.

name: Haatan
description: A former member of the secret demon organization Chrono Kreuz, counted among its elite Numbers agents. Tries to act uncaring, but a good kid at heart who stands up for justice for demons in defiance of the Aesir gods.

name: War God Valvatorez
description: The essence of demon and deity, tempered with the unique power of a true protagonist, infused all at once into Valvatorez. His secret to controlling this tempest of clashing powers? His love of sardines, of course!

name: Magical Beauty Etna
description: Etna, who has become younger in both appearance and heart. She claims to be a first-grader at Netherworld Elementary, but rumor has it that her strength and greed are still at the level of a Majin.

name: Pure Avatar Flonne
description: Fallen Avatar Flonne, having been awakened to a new form through a reality-altering magic. Her immense latent mana and strong feelings for others created a transformation bursting with Love Power.

name: Casual Love Oracle
description: Love Oracle, donning the ultimate 'casual outfit' designed with the theme of a Magic Cutie's attire. Crafted after a million trials, it's the crystallization of love... or perhaps obsessive fandom.

name: Pure Sicily XENO
description: Sicily XENO as the unexpected new recruit of the magic cutie team, the Pure Pures! Her designated color is blue. Her transformation catchphrase is something she obsessed over every night before drifting to sleep.

name: Magical Asagi
description: Asagi Koigiri, transformed into a Magic Cutie by the power of premonition. Normally, she'd never wear such an outfit, making her 1000000% embarrassed, but she endures it and fights on with all her might!

name: Classical Emizel
description: The Netherworld President, in charge of the Hades Reform Anniversary Festival. The baton in his hand is purely for show because it looks cool, he's a complete novice at conducting!

name: Flame Dancer Piyori
description: Piyori, equipped with the 'DX Prism Drum' that has the power to purge evil thoughts, has arrived in Hades. It's said that demons purified by this drum become pure-hearted and demure.

name: Lanzarote
description: Once a popular Netherworld idol, she is rumored to have been outshined by the female Laharl. Lately, her activities have been on the decline, but she's said to have a special musical power... though the details are a secret~☆

name: Punk Rock Fuka
description: Fuka, who became a punk rocker after watching late-night TV. She's a beginner at guitar, but the noise she makes is already ear-splitting. The spirit of punk rock resides within her... or so she says.

name: Songstress Rozalin
description: Thanks to the resume Mom sent and Yeyasu's backing, Rozalin made her debut as a songstress. Even as a newcomer, she's already as popular as a top idol!

name: Beach Hanako
description: To compete in the "Volleybomb" Tournament, Hanako joined the fray in a swimsuit that's easy to move in. She chose it together with Etna, claiming they're similar in size.

name: Beach Thunderlady Laharl
description: Thunderlord Laharl mysteriously transformed into a Thunderlady while out at the beach. Apparently this Laharl is thrilled to spend some quality bonding together with Sicily Xeno as sisters for a change.

name: Beach Liezerota
description: To compete in the "Volleybomb" Tournament, Liezerota donned a sporty new swimsuit. With her surprising innate athleticism, she’s sure to captivate the audience!

name: Beach Melodia
description: To compete in the "Volleybomb" Tournament with Zed, Melodia donned a new swimsuit. With her dynamite beach wear, she’s sure to capture Zed's attention♥!

name: Yukata Flonne
description: Flonne dressed in a traditional Hinomoto-style yukata to celebrate the Haunt Springs Festival. Pirilika helped her put it on, but if it comes undone, she doesn't know how to fix it herself!

name: Beach Ao
description: Ao wearing a custom swimsuit made by Pirilika. It combines ease of movement with cuteness, making it one of Ao's most treasured possessions.

name: Beach Nisa
description: Vanquishing all evil that lurks in the demonic summer! The ultimate hero of justice, Nisa! She serves up safety more by the seashore!

name: Yukata Pirilika
description: Pirilika slipped into a yukata just in time for the Haunt Springs Festival! She’s a practiced otaku when it comes to putting on yukata and other Hinomoto-style outfits - her record is apparently under 0.1 seconds!

name: Summer Seraphina
description: Seraphina decked out in a 1000% pure and demure look, taking her cues from Artina's personal style. With this new look, she’s sure to catch Sir Killia's eye!
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Magistrate Akuma
description: A Magistrate of Hinomoto who sees himself as Fuji's rival. An unparalled master of the sacred art of ping-pong who rose to his title solely on his table tennis prowess. It's a shame that outside of ping-pong, he's utterly useless.

name: Fearleader Higan Zesshosai
description: Higan Zesshosai, clad in a Fearleader costume. She agreed to cheer from the sidelines in exchange for a 400-year supply of sweets, but she yearns to join the exciting matches unfolding right in front of her.

name: Volleyball Queen Fuka XENO
description: Fuka XENO clad in an outfit suited for the Woelympics Volleybomb competition. Her physical abilities have suddenly skyrocketed, but it's a mystery as to how.

name: Malefic Archdemon Overlord Zenon
description: A being born from Fake Zenon's undying grudge. Though Adell and Rozalin helped to overcome that hatred, this wraith still lingers on...

name: Tennis Tyrant Seraphina XENO
class_name_5: Demonic Butterfly of the Tennis Court
description: Seraphina XENO dressed in an athletic outfit for any type of sport. It seems this provocative fashion choice increases the effectiveness of her "Balor Gaze".
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Tino Shade
description: An energetic member of the Hunter clan, "First Steps". She is a dedicated Rank 4 Solo Hunter and looks up to her guild Master, Kray, as if he was a god.

name: Liz Smart
description: The older sister of Sitri, and Tino's mentor. As her epithet suggests, she boasts god-like speed that leaves no shadow behind. When she starts using cutesy nicknames, be wary of a whole new level of danger.

name: Thousand Kills Sicily XENO
description: Sicily XENO, impressed with Krai Andrey, decided to try her hand at being a Relic user too. Unknown to her, she quickly became much more skilled than him, not that it's a high bar to clear.

name: Krai Andrey
description: The Top-Ranking Level 8 Treasure Hunter who leads the clan called the "Grieving Souls". He is known by his second name of "Thousand Tricks" for his cunning ways, but in reality he's a fraud with no actual talent or motivation and just wants to retire from the adventurer life.

name: Citri Smart
description: The younger sister of Liz and one of Krai's childhood friends. Once hailed as "The Prodigy" alchemist, she could solve any scientific mystery without fail until that one fateful day...

name: Sardia
description: Sardia's first appearance after a 20-year hiatus since the first Disgaea game. This demonic knight who attempted to snatch Laharl's Overlord title is said to be able to slay any demon with her blade... probably.

name: Formal Flonne
description: Flonne is all dressed up to host the 5th Anniversary bash! Each decoration on her dress was handcrafted by Pirilika, and it's said to represent all the Love that Flonne has poured into her mission over the last 5 years, enhancing her strength.

name: Battle Ceremonial Garb Usalia
class_name_3: Black Rabbit Lurking in the 5th Anniversary
class_name_5: Black Twin Moons Dyeing the Fearsome Banquet
description: Usalia in her full-power form during the Netherworld invasion. Wrapping the power given by Xenon in her ceremonial garb, she sweeps away the enemies before her alongside Seraphina.

name: Formal Laharl
description: Laharl all suited up in formal wear for a change for the 5th Anniversary! The outfit he had custom-tailored a few months ago bears more than a small resemblance to his father's style.

name: Formal Pleinair
description: The true majestic Ms. Pleinair hidden within, she is the absolute authority who can establish all the rules of the world! Apparently, the reason everyone always calls her "Ms." is one of her rules.

name: Dance Battle Ceremonial Garb Seraphina
class_name_3: White Rabbit Dancing in the 5th Anniversary
class_name_5: White Twin Moons Dancing in the Mad Banquet
description: Seraphina in her full-power form during the Netherworld invasion. Wearing ceremonial garb that fully draws out her power of madness, she tramples the enemies before her alongside Usalia.

name: Santa Salvatore
description: Salvatore dressed in a Santa costume. Even during Christmas, she doesn't waver as she goes around giving demons presents in the form of orders.

name: Remilia
class_name_5: Top Disciple of the Abyss Witch
description: A student witch attending the magic school Majimaji. She was destined to lose her life in a summoning magic accident, but has a past where she was saved by Majorene and others.

name: Santa Frostlord Rozalin
class_name_4: Thorn Princess Blooming in the Holy Night
class_name_5: Azure Rose of the Holy Night Soaring Through the Sky
description: Ice Emperor Rozalin dressed in a Santa costume. She can transform using a spell given to her by Remilia. 'Lovely Kuudere ChaArctiaBot(talk)nge'

name: Santa Majolene
class_name_5: Abyss Witch Guiding the Holy Night
description: Majorene dressed in a Santa costume. With a design resembling a youkai kindergarten smock, according to supervisor Remilia, 'I have no regrets!'

name: Santa Lucy
class_name_5: Red Fallen Angel Shaking the Holy Night
description: Lucy dressed in a Santa costume. Though the outfit is risqué, she designed it herself and is enthusiastically wearing it.

name: Santa Artina
class_name_5: Messenger of the Holy Night Coming with Light
description: Artina wearing a Santa costume prepared by Celestia. To deliver presents to 'bad children,' she diligently works even on Christmas without taking a break.

name: Formal Desco
class_name_5: Ultimate Weapon of the New Year
description: Desco wearing a matching kimono with Fuka. With equipment bought after begging Genjuro, she will conquer New Year's together with Fuka.

name: Formal Fuka
description: Fuka wearing a matching kimono with Desco. With a kimono chosen after 10 hours of shopping, she will conquer New Year's together with Desco.

name: New Year's Kimono Saint Etna
class_name_3: First Shrine Visit in Another World
class_name_5: Celestial Maiden Descending in the Dawn Light
description: Saint Etna dressed in a New Year's kimono. With a design reminiscent of a celestial maiden wearing a feather robe, it is said to bring good fortune to surrounding worshippers.

name: Shrine Maiden Piyori
description: Piyori dressed in a self-made shrine maiden outfit. She's secretly excited about experiencing her dream of being a shrine maiden. By the way, she pronounces 'omochi' (rice cake) as 'oMOOchi'.

name: Uniform Seraphina
description: Sapphire dressed in the Evil Academy uniform. As the heiress to the Rhodonite family, she finds Almaz's denseness frustrating... according to the setting.

name: Uniform Ao
class_name_4: Loving Daughter Who Thinks of Her Father
class_name_5: Ice Fang Princess Offering Pure Love
description: Ao wearing a uniform, currently on a trial enrollment at Evil Academy. She's looking forward to the open house that coincides with Valentine's Day... according to the setting.

name: School Uniform Liezerota
class_name_4: Childhood Friend with Strong Gap Appeal
description: Liezerota in a school uniform. Her makeup, different from usual, was done by Seraphina. She's aiming for Killia's heart with the gap between this and her usual look... according to the setting.

name: Evil Teacher Valvatorez
description: Valvatorez appointed as an evil teacher at Evil Academy. A perfect evil teacher who can teach any difficult subject as long as it involves sardines... according to the setting.

name: Uniform Girl Laharl
description: Laharl-chan who was turned into a sexy gal by magic. Her clothes, makeup, and even hair styling are all maintained by magic, and it's said she can't even take off these clothes in this form...

name: Hero Ash
description: A young man from a world different from the Netherworld called 'Ivoire'. He is a 'Phantom', a soul without a physical body, and continues to protect Marona who became a hero.

name: Henna
description: The former queen of the kingdom of 'Hasara' on the Isle of Sand. A female 'Phantom', a soul that loves freedom. She is a user of the enchanting ability 'Opera Mauve'.
cv_name: ブリドカットセーラ恵美

name: Maronash
description: The form of Marona and Ash after performing a Bond Confine. The water dragon ability possessed by Ash now dwells within Marona, allowing her to demonstrate abilities beyond her limits.

name: Hero Marona
description: A girl from a world different from the Netherworld called 'Ivoire'. She has the ability to communicate with souls called 'Phantoms', and is called a 'Hero' for having defeated the God of Destruction.

name: Apricot
description: The daughter of the heroic pirate 'Argent', and a 'Phantom' girl who succeeded him as captain. She possesses the ability 'Daydream' that purifies souls.

name: Songstress Seashore
description: Seashore wrapped in an idol costume made by Piyori, aiming to join the Pure Pures. She blows up the hearts and bodies of the audience with her explosive charm.

name: Fuji Zessho-sai
description: The form of Fuji with his potential abilities drawn out to the extreme. As a result of the sudden awakening of power he was supposed to obtain in the future, he thinks about nothing but Ao even more than before.

name: Nitra
description: An angel who was once helped by Fuji and others. She's Seashore's best friend, and it's said that when it comes to Seashore, her usually gentle demeanor completely changes.

name: Songstress Officer Sakura
description: An idol once scouted by Wayasu, who became one of the Thirteen Officers through steady hard work. A complete villain who uses extremely despicable methods with a straight face... pure-hearted type★

name: Love Songstress Flonne
description: Pure Flonne who has awakened as an idol by drawing out her potential abilities. It is said that her passionate love songs enchant all who hear them...

name: Fenrich XENO
description: Fenrich from another world who serves Lord Hakanakun. He is feared by his subordinates as someone whose thoughts behind his smile are unpredictable.

name: Rabbit Demon King Usaria
description:
Usaria dressed in her father and mother's costumes.
I vow to overcome the tragic past and become stronger,
In both his name and reality, he became the demon king of the Rabbit Demon World.

name: Maid Rozalin
description: Rozalin dressed in a maid outfit. She has been polishing her housekeeping skills for Adell on a daily basis, and it is said that her aptitude as a maid is actually impeccable.

name: Maid Beryl XENO
description:
Raspberyl XENO dressed in maid outfit.
The maid is in a position where he is left to the housework.
She enjoys stinking about new maids.

name: Liam
description:
Young head of the Count Banfield family.
He lived a good life and had an unreasonable end.
Based on the reflection of his past life, he aims to become a "unscrupulous lord"...

name: The son-in-law, Lahar-chan
description:
By chance, the Thunder Emperor Lahar, turned into a woman,
She appears in a groom costume. Just attendees.
He is excited to be able to get even closer to his younger sister.

name: Tier
description:
She is the first princess of the Holy Kingdom of Libe and protects the kingdom.
"Princess Knight." Since Liam saved me,
He pledges fanatic and absolute loyalty to him.

name: Bride Raspberyl
description:
A bride outfit given to me by Sapphire
Raspberyl is a bit confused, dressed in her arms.
She looks cute, but she is still a participant.

name: Swimsuit Majorita
description:
Majorita is in a swimsuit and is operating behind the scenes on the beach.
This is a handmade swimsuit designed with great care,
He apparently secretly likes it himself too.

name: Swimsuit Pi
description:
Piyori dressed in a sporty swimsuit.
As a lifeguard who protects the peace of the beach,
It will bring you all life-saving power!

name: Sunburned Amane
description:
Amane is tanned by the intense heat of the heat.
His burnt skin is the sea-spirit protecting the sea
He is said to be proud of his efforts.

description: Prism Red of the Prism Rangers. The hot-blooded one with a strong sense of justice.

description: Prism Blue of the Prism Rangers. He's the cool one and was once Red's Rival.

name: Prism Orange

class_name_5: 魔界の超人気アイドル

A super popular and beautiful idol in the demon world who can sing and dance.

description:
He is one of the Ten Demon Kings of the Todoroki Demon World, known as the Great Powers.
After fighting each other, he survived and gained the status of a demon general.
Now a faithful servant of the Demon Emperor Void Dark.

name: Ponchos
description:
A former heir to Red Magnus, the Demon King of the Scratching Demon World.
He lost all his patience with the selfish demon king and joined Lost.
He holds a grudge for being used all the time.

name: Logan
description:
The demon king of the blood-thirsty demon world, feared as the "throwing demon king."
However, he is now old, so he cannot continue his physical strength.
He has a grudge of Lost being taken away by everything.

name: Warrior
description: A warrior with a strong body and an indomitable spirit. A professional at close quarters combat.

name: Lady Fighter
description: A female warrior with both flexibility and strength. Excels at one-point blitzkrieg combat.

name: Martial Artist
description: A martial artist who has mastered the physical arts. His unique attire is a traditional costume that  is testament to the legacy of his ancestors.

name: Fight Mistress
description: A female martial artist with fancy skills. She hails from the small frontier world, the "Village of Beasts".

description: A priest that punishes himself while healing others. He is a sensible person  who has no prejudice against humans or angels.

name: Cleric
description: A priestess who heals her wounded companions. She follows the scriptures of Vinaya  and is always meditating.

name: Archeress
description: A kind-hearted hunter of the Netherworld. She has a kind of precognition to accurately  predict the wind speed and direction.

name: Thief
description: A thief who risks her life to collect treasures. Second to none when it comes to stealing.

name: Maid
description: A faithful maid to her master. The accuracy of her work is not good enough, but she looks cute when she is focused on her work.

name: Gunner
description: A gunman who dispatches his enemies with quick movement. He has the trust of his friends, but he does  not talk much and prefers to be alone.

name: Ninja
description: A cold-hearted assassin who lives in the shadows. He specializes in his unique fighting technique, "Ninja Art".

name: Lady Samurai
description: A sword maiden who exorcises demons. Her clan guards the sanctuary around the Gate of Celestia, the door that connects the Netherworld and Celestia.

name: Armor Knight
description: A knight of steel who boasts an ironclad defense. Admired by children for wielding her sword  and protecting her master.

name: Magic Swordsman
description:
He is a swordsman but also a supernatural ability who controls magic.
He is a rare entity, said to be a handful of demons.

name: Professor
description: A researcher of magic science. It's said that great cares are taken on experiment subjects.

name: 賢者女
description:
A child of wisdom raised by a great demon tree that lives for 100 million years.
He can hear the sounds of plants and is also close to the fairies.

name: Wrestler
description: A warrior who spends his days fighting the strong. He excels at fighting in pairs.

name: Pirate
description: A pirate who runs through the vast universe. He excels at long-range sniping.

name: Dark Knight
description: A knight in black who controls the darkness. The jet-black flames flickering in the depths of his eyes  would bring the fear of death to anyone who sees the flames.

name: Ninja women
description:
A beautiful kunoichi dances in the darkness.
He tosses his enemies with his illusionary movements.

name: The sorcerer
description:
A user of Jujutsu who sways misfortune.
Have a unique definition of good and evil and the good fortune of others
He believes that control is his mission.

name: 陰陽術師
description:
A surgeon who controls the field with his unique abilities.
Power is often seen as low in all demonic worlds,
Many also evaluate the hidden potential of that ability.

name: The monster user
description:
A wild warrior living with monsters.
Passionate about cultivating the best monsters
I've been burning and have cultivated a wealth of knowledge and
No one can stand out in technology.

name: Masked Hero
description:
An unknown, self-proclaimed hero.
When it comes to running away, it's unparalleled.

name: Android
description:
Female-style combat weapons.
Special metals are used for armor.
It is highly durable and can move flexibly.

name: Bouncer
description:
A guardian in a black suit.
If you want to protect your master, you can become a shield yourself.
He has a spirit.

name: Battle Suit
description:
A combat power suit developed by humanity.
It greatly increases the abilities of the worn person.

name: Gusterk soldier
description:
Empire soldiers developed in the cold regions of the human world.
Apparently, the armor that wraps around her entire body cannot be worn alone.

name: Lekidna soldier
description:
A soldier from a kingdom that developed in the desert region of the human world.
My legs and hips are strong thanks to training in sand.

name: Celestial Host
description: Heavenly soldier specializing in battle. He upholds the heavenly law and  ruthlessly eliminates those who oppose it.

name: Celestial Hostess
description: A female soldier who protects the celestial peace. Because of her firm beliefs, she is a bit stubborn in certain ways.

name: 死人海賊
description:
The killed demon is manipulated as a dead man.
They have no intentions, they just fight as they say.
