name: Usalia
description: Toto Bunny Overlord, affected by the curse of berserk. She suppresses the curse by eating curry. She's a well-behaved girl with a strong will.

name: Raspberyl
description: She's a graduate of Evil Academy and now a Delinquent Teacher. She's a super Delinquent who works every day raising money, donating blood, and engaging in volunteer work. A life rebelling against demon conventions sure looks cool.

name: Desco
description: A girl created to destroy the world. Her dream is to become the strongest Final Boss in the world. She admires Fuka as her Big Sis.

name: Death Zet
description:
The final boss created by Fusai Genjuro,
The perfect version of the final weapon DESCO.
The real culprit who hated and killed Fuka.

name: Prinny Curtis
description:
Green Pliny is active as the Earth Hero.
He is making an effort to add a "sus" to the end of his words.

name: Pringer V3
description: The deadliest robot ever found in the Prinny world. Only disciplined Prinnies can become robots... It looks just like a Prinny, but it doesn't explode when thrown.

name: Hagos
description:
The Demon World President reigns at the top of the devils.
He is also Emizel's father.
Is he the one who corrupted the demon world?

name: Thursday
description: An all-purpose robot made by Jennifer. It is equipped with a computerized voice and a self-destruct mechanism.

name: Taro
description: A timid and cynical person, Adell's younger brother. He has horns on his head due to the curse of Overlord Zenon. He admires and respects Rozalin.

name: Hanako
description: The younger sister of Adell and Taro, who's shy but energetic. She has wings on her back due to the curse of Overlord Zenon. Despite her young age, her cooking skills are on par with the professionals.

name: Tink
description: Rozalin's childhood friend and subordinate of Overlord Zenon. He used to be a handsome boy, but somehow was turned into a frog.

name: Red Tink
description: Rozalin's childhood friend and subordinate of Overlord Zenon. Normally a gentle demon, but when enraged, he becomes violent and dangerous.

name: Burkano
description:
The angel chief is jealous of his favorite Archangel Fron.
He loses himself in ambition and anger and goes out of control.

name: Kurtis
description: He was caught up in an incident and lost 70% of his body. He's a cyborg who calls himself the Defender of Earth.

name: Lamington
description:
The ruler of Celestia, the counterpart of the Netherworld.
A beautiful angel filled with love and kindness who cares about the Netherworld as much as Celestia.

name: Don Joaquin
description:
The first demon world hero.
Unable to fulfill his mission, his regrets become his soul and wander around the demon world.

name: Mid-Boss
description: A mysterious demon who's often called Mid-Boss by Laharl and his friends. He calls himself Vyers the Dark Adonis, but that name is not generally accepted by others.

name: Ms. Raspberyl
description: She's a graduate of Evil Academy and now a Delinquent Teacher. She's a super Delinquent who works every day raising money, donating blood, and engaging in volunteer work. A life rebelling against demon conventions sure looks cool.

name: Overlord Priere
description: An Overlord who travels through many Netherworlds in search of powerful opponents. Though once a holy lady, she succumbed to the thirst for power which transformed her into an Overlord.

name: Santa Usalia
class_name_1: Rabbit Overlord of the Holy Night
class_name_2: Rabbit Overlord of the Holy Night
description: It's nice to get dressed, but Usalia doesn't know what Christmas is all about. So she decides to go distribute curry.

name: Mirror Cake Prinny
description: Prinnies that look happy. But their actual condition is too dark to divulge...

name: Gym Shorts Raspberyl
description: Raspberyl in short shorts  is going to take part in the Fest-evil of Sport. She never misses a prep session before sports  and always makes sure the members of Team Evil are prepared as well.

name: Overlord Asagi
description:
The evil Overlord that rules the world of "Disgaea Wars (Tentative)".
With her absolute power,
she dominates the world, threatening all its denizens.

name: Creator Asagi
description:
The genius girl who developed the game Disgaea Wars (Tentative).
In order to develop interesting games,
her brain is always running at full capacity. For her, a continuous intake of sugar is a must!

name: Swimsuit Desco
description:
Desco, who is in her special swimsuit and can dive for an extremely long time.
She loves to leave only her fin above the surface of the water,
pretending to be a shark.

name: Desco XENO
description:
Another Desco from another world.
She's been working hard to help Fuka XENO.
Rumor has it that she has already become the final boss in her world?

name: Swimsuit Prinny
description:
A Prinny who is determined to enjoy his summer vacation,
but his summer vacation
is doomed to be torture...

name: Attired Prinny
description: A prinny wearing his attire to commemorate the first anniversary of Disgaea RPG. This Prinny's back looks slightly straighter than usual, perhaps because of this splendid attire.

name: Dark Santa Usalia
description:
Usalia inherits Laharl's Dark Santa Suit and becomes ruthless.
No longer confined by her amiable disposition, she is incredibly powerful.

name: Liezerota
description:
A very gentle-looking woman.
She is the daughter of Goldion the Great Demon Fist, and the elder sister of Void.
She treats Killia like family.

name: Saint Etna
description:
Another Etna from another world.
Despite being a demon, she has a gentle disposition and a heart of gold.
Her saintly voice has surprised even Prinnies.

name: Sakuya
description:
A battle-hardened nine-tailed fox who has made divination her life's work.
She is a troublemaker, as she will curse those who get terrible divination results, and grant her favor to those who get ideal results.

name: Beatrice
description: A girl who acts as Caretaker of the Forbidden Library in the mansion where Emilia and her friends live.

name: Demonic Rem
description: Rem who released her power as a demon. All her stats have improved and she will not forgive those who are judged to be enemies.

name: Demonic Flonne
description: Flonne was inspired by Rem who released the power of the demon. Dressed in a costume brought from nowhere, she feels like a cool demon!

name: Pringer X
description:
The pinnacle of ancient civilizations.
This legendary Prinny-shaped robot is a killing machine as it has shed blood in countless battles.

name: Tink XENO
description:
Emizel XENO's childhood friend whose head is always filled with thoughts of social success.
He has many minions at his disposal through his use of gold and violence.

name: Fallen Vessel Flonne
description:
A formidable individual even within the mysterious XENO group.
She goes by the name of Fallen Vessel Flonne and apparently has a troubled past with Saint Etna.

name: Tria
description:
Daughter of an oppressive lord, she defies his tyrannical rule and now lives on the run from his assassins.
Only that's her character's backstory, as she plays the lead actress in the Love Laboratory.

name: Swimsuit Raspberyl
description:
Raspberyl has arrived at the beach to inspect check out the School of the Weirdo.
The Prinny boat she always carries with her is an extraordinary boat Mao himself rebuilt!

name: Des X
description:
The Final Boss and the Perfect Version of the Final Weapon DESCO that Genjuro Kazamatsuri created for his daughter Fuka.
The true culprit responsible for turning Fuka into a Prinny.

name: スーパーデスコ
description:
未来のバトルスーツによって
最終兵器として新たな能力を手に入れたデスコ。
現代の主人公たちを救うべく今立ち上がる。

name: 殺戮兵器プリニー
description:
全身が鋼鉄でできた未来のプリニー。
戦闘面も高性能となっており、
語尾には金属音っぽい「ッＳＵ」をつける。

name: サンタリーゼロッタ
description:
クリスマスパーティーを盛り上げるため
サンタ服を身にまとったリーゼロッタ。
今回の衣装はリーゼロッタのお手製。がお～！

name: 干支フーカ
description:
厳しいラブ修行と天性の思い込み力で
２０２２年の干支である
寅の力を手に入れたフーカ。

name: 魔王ロザリンド
description:
魔王プリエの衣装に袖を通したロザリンド。
強大な闘気により内に秘めたナニカが触発、
すべてを圧倒する力を手に入れた。

name: メタリカ
description:
沼を司る自称天才魔女。
他の生物を寄せ付けぬ程の瘴気を
発する沼のほとりに住んでいる。

name: 百騎兵
description:
メタリカが異世界より召喚した
魔法生物（マナニア）。
圧倒的な力を持つ魔神のはずだが……

name: ネザリア
description:
ヴァルプルギスの夜会の議長を務める魔女。
霧を扱う魔法に長けており、
その実力は当代随一とされている。

name: 魔女式ラハールちゃん
description:
メタリカの衣装を纏ったラハールちゃん。
偉大なる沼の魔女の力を手にした彼女は
もはや誰にも止めることはできない。

name: Love Zed
description:
マオが開発した超魔熱血恋愛細胞をその身に宿し
身近にあった親子愛や姉妹愛を切っ掛けとして、
あらゆる愛に目覚めたデスゼットの新たな姿。

name: Flonnezilla
